  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Open surgery and CO2 laser surgery are both established treatment modalities for T1N0 glottic
      carcinoma. It is controversial for T1N0 glottic carcinoma with anterior commissure involved.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
