  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  T1N0 SCC of glottic carcinoma with anterior commissure involve

          -  No nodal metastasis and distant metastasis

          -  All patients must have CT/MR and electronic laryngoscope test before surgery and after
             surgery

          -  Expected lifetime&gt;1 year

          -  Patients and families agreed to participate in the test and sign the informed consent

          -  Without cognitive impairment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  With severe cardiac insufficiency Liver and kidney function is not complete systemic
             infection patients

          -  Patients with pregnancy and lactation

          -  Have surgery contraindications
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
